# ChromaMark — integrations & ecosystem review

::: info Purpose
An honest feasibility pass over the 11 wishlist ideas: what's genuinely
possible, what's constrained, rough effort/impact, and a suggested order. Written
in ChromaMark so you can review it in the VS Code preview or the playground.
Everything here is a proposal — nothing is built yet.
:::

